{"tid":985944,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖慎入］暗瘡凹洞 爛面想死","createTime":"2019-01-18T05:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T15:52:47.000Z","uid":161621,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce637f60f5ff37743c89c2cdd9aedaeaab7c90a","tid":985944,"uid":161621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"中一就開始生暗瘡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣聽屋企人講大個就無暗瘡 又無錢醫<br />\n所以一直無理到 但發現生咗咁多年好似無好到 開始理返皮膚個陣已經爛得無得再爛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家變爛面 啲凹洞都唔知有無得搞 真係sad到爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n20歲 想知有無得搞返好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為照鏡望著自己真係想一野轟爆塊鏡 完全無自信 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慎入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3396a2e90eca042de4fdb55975612ba6ec415608","tid":985944,"uid":77569,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cf1625df34a9ab5e3eb96fd47b8f39630bf753d","tid":985944,"uid":48235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"有錢就去做激光啦"},{"pid":"b83b80dee9c9b3ca8334ed41086bdd08efc8101f","tid":985944,"uid":202354,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ce637f60f5ff37743c89c2cdd9aedaeaab7c90a","tid":985944,"uid":161621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"中一就開始生暗瘡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣聽屋企人講大個就無暗瘡 又無錢醫<br />\n所以一直無理到 但發現生咗咁多年好似無好到 開始理返皮膚個陣已經爛得無得再爛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家變爛面 啲凹洞都唔知有無得搞 真係sad到爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n20歲 想知有無得搞返好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為照鏡望著自己